Dobro jutro, tata!
Tata, probudi se!

00:02:17.763 --> 00:02:20.641
Tata, probudi se!
Probudi se, tata!

00:02:21.058 --> 00:02:23.560
Probudi se, tata.

00:02:23.644 --> 00:02:27.356
Tata! Tata! Tata! Tata!
Probudi se!

00:02:28.816 --> 00:02:30.526
Grisl! Koliko je sati?

00:02:30.984 --> 00:02:34.196
Danas je Trolstis!

00:02:34.488 --> 00:02:38.492
Trolstis!
Jedan dan da budemo srećni!

00:02:38.659 --> 00:02:40.994
Da!

00:02:42.329 --> 00:02:44.665
Trolove! Trolove!

00:02:51.004 --> 00:02:55.926
Dajte aplauz za vašeg čuvara
trolova, vašu ministarku sreće,

00:02:56.009 --> 00:02:59.304
